Class ScopeStack.ReverseIterator

  • Object
    • ScopeStack.ReverseIterator

    Iterator<Scope>
    Enclosing class:

    class ScopeStack.ReverseIterator
extends Object
implements Iterator<Scope>
    An iterator that iterates in reverse order. For use on an array that is intended to represent a stack. Does not implement the remove() method.
